{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/MainContextProtocol\/iteration(mayBlock:)"},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"iteration","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"mayBlock"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"extendedModule":"GLib","roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"iteration(mayBlock:)","externalID":"s:4GLib19MainContextProtocolPAAE9iteration8mayBlockS2b_tF","symbolKind":"method"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Runs a single iteration for the given main loop."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/maincontextprotocol\/iteration(mayblock:)"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"iteration"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"mayBlock","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This involves"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"checking to see if any event sources are ready to be processed,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"then if no events sources are ready and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"mayBlock"},{"type":"text","text":" is true, waiting"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"for a source to